# Spec Evolution Log

A high-level audit trail of requirement and specification changes.

## Format

Each entry should follow this structure:

```
[DATE] [CHANGE TYPE] [Reference] - Description
  Reason: Why the change was made
  Impact: What was affected
```

## Change Types

- ADDED: New requirement or spec introduced
- MODIFIED: Existing requirement changed
- REMOVED: Requirement removed
- SUPERSEDED: Requirement replaced by another

